    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in fair condition. The interior shows moderate wear including worn upholstery and some scuffs on trim surfaces. The exterior has several scratches and minor dents visible on multiple panels. Mechanically the car runs but may have some issues that should be inspected before purchase. No recent major repairs on record.",
